{"tid":797121,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本內衣品牌實驗証明白裇衫配白BRA更有透視效果","createTime":"2018-08-28T09:19:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-28T10:26:09.000Z","uid":55981,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"fab73c7d5ee7739a5bb8a4802a594c3e8a245b2b","tid":797121,"uid":55981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T09:19:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180828/640_f20ab1f555590d4acd14ac4107bc3358.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180828%2F640_f20ab1f555590d4acd14ac4107bc3358.jpg&h=11e2e9f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n白色的制服要穿白色內衣才比較不明顯？真的是這樣嗎？<br />\n<br />\n日韓有許多學校規定，女學生穿制服時得搭配白色內衣，理由是因為穿相同顏色，這樣內衣才不會太明顯透出來，但事實卻好像並非如此！日本一內衣品牌就做了實驗，他們準備了白色、粉紅色、水藍色、皮膚色、紅色以及深藍色的色塊布料，放在膚色的背景上，再用白色的布料蓋上去，實驗看看哪種顏色會顯得最明顯。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180828/640_c77ce25c7bef1359fec9a5fa795cbf8a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180828%2F640_c77ce25c7bef1359fec9a5fa795cbf8a.jpg&h=dc3c718b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180828/640_c58111a30d4e6792d55be7b9fe6a514a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180828%2F640_c58111a30d4e6792d55be7b9fe6a514a.jpg&h=3473125a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n結果赫然發現，白色、粉紅色、水藍色等淺色系的色塊反而比深色區的紅色、深藍色更加明顯，讓該內衣廠在推特呼籲「希望讓大家改掉『白色＋白色比較不會透』的觀念！」（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）"},{"pid":"b9843fb7c1c082d34a0dc9bf4702845e60ed2551","tid":797121,"uid":3241,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T09:24:14.000Z","msg":"send比全港男訓導主任要求強制執行著白色內衣指引先"},{"pid":"31dbf3b5bae56b30569b5f0b5b164b1b9ae093f9","tid":797121,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T09:25:57.000Z","msg":"黑提唔洗帶bra"},{"pid":"8843db17640a58fc7a8630b757bb7429866c0851","tid":797121,"uid":108467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9843fb7c1c082d34a0dc9bf4702845e60ed2551","tid":797121,"uid":3241,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T09:24:14.000Z","msg":"send比全港男訓導主任要求強制執行著白色內衣指引先"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T09:26:11.000Z","msg":"唔send正仆街"},{"pid":"dc5035bdd03c277745a527115e9a910a10bdcd47","tid":797121,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T09:26:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02ce2cbf20c02dccec3b149d5b818c31539d9766","tid":797121,"uid":86756,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T09:27:34.000Z","msg":"呀sir做野唔使你教！"},{"pid":"0e197beedda7192c9b369ba3de3b37c908add760","tid":797121,"uid":11840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9843fb7c1c082d34a0dc9bf4702845e60ed2551","tid":797121,"uid":3241,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T09:24:14.000Z","msg":"send比全港男訓導主任要求強制執行著白色內衣指引先"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T09:28:37.000Z","msg":"唔係執行左好耐架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39f4bc559ebd3724acb1699df2ead841b39e20ba","tid":797121,"uid":4964,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"0e197beedda7192c9b369ba3de3b37c908add760","tid":797121,"uid":11840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9843fb7c1c082d34a0dc9bf4702845e60ed2551","tid":797121,"uid":3241,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T09:24:14.000Z","msg":"send比全港男訓導主任要求強制執行著白色內衣指引先"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T09:28:37.000Z","msg":"唔係執行左好耐架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T09:38:38.000Z","msg":"唔怪得以前中學啲女戴黑bra會比訓導問候<br />\n原來想透啲"},{"pid":"1ddfc5df57edea12e7c8048fa1d2ce74b52650db","tid":797121,"uid":65128,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T09:43:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"p